metadata.name: Māia I
metadata.description:
"Māia I" is an NFT of a physical painting by Dom Baker and also the first collaboration with fellow kiwi NFT artist Pete May. The tā moko (Māori tattoo) designs on this painting are original hand drawings created by Pete May. 

This NFT is a 1/1 artwork. It is also one of a pair, the other 1/1 NFT being 
"Māia II" by Dom Baker.

The sale is for the NFT only. Physical artwork sold separately.
